===算囤===
*將總胡數減12再除3，其商數即就為囤的分數，然後依稱為半名堂的牌型，對分數先加後乘，成為總分。半名堂如下表<ref name="跑胡子规则技巧">{{Cite news|url=http://www.51v.cn/Article/jsll_200918_09181640362AFG7717FDGIAG79J07A_3089/|title=跑胡子规则技巧|language=zh-cn|publisher=湖北游戏中心|author=|date=|accessdate=2013-09-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130821112846/http://www.51v.cn/Article/jsll_200918_09181640362AFG7717FDGIAG79J07A_3089/|archivedate=2013-08-21}}</ref>。
